'''Pixelux Entertainment''' is a software developing company founded in [[October]] [[2003]].

On [[May 8]], [[2006]], [[LucasArts]] announced its partnership with Pixelux Entertainment, through which LucasArts will incorporate Pixelux's [http://www.pixeluxentertainment.com/index.cfm?link=technology Digital Molecular Matter] (DMM) technology into all internal titles currently in development for next-generation [[Star Wars video games|video game]] consoles, including ''[[Star Wars: The Force Unleashed]]''.<ref name="LucasArts">{{LucasArtsCite|url=press/releases/108.html|text=LucasArts and Pixelux Redefine Environmental Realism for Next-Generation Interactive Entertainment}}</ref>

